1.2
log
@Add gpio(4) support for omap3/4 and am335x.

Feedback by patrick and syl, tested by syl on BeagleBoard and BBB.
ok syl@@
@
text
@/* $OpenBSD: omgpiovar.h,v 1.1 2013/09/04 14:38:31 patrick Exp $ */
/*
